" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 621px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Grade V liver laceration",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 601px; height: 237px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The CT scan of the upper abdomen (A) shows a grade V complex liver laceration of the right lobe of the liver. The contrast difference between normal and injured tissue is better seen in the magnified, narrowed window (B). The &nbsp;linear and extensive nature of this pattern, which involves segments IV, V, and VI, is described as a 'bear claw injury.'",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"     CT: computed tomography.",
"    </div>",
